<subSubSection pageNumber="366" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="366">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="366">Note:</emphasis>
This is the 
<typeStatus>generitype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Buphthalmum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="366">Buphthalmum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but, through an error, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Buphthalmum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aquaticum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="366">B. aquaticum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was incorrectly listed as the 
<typeStatus>generitype</typeStatus>
by Jarvis &amp; al. (
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="366">Regnum Veg.</emphasis>
127: 27. 1993), instead of 
<taxonomicName authority="L." authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Buphthalmum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="salicifolium">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="366">B. salicifolium</emphasis>
L.
</taxonomicName>
, as noted by Greuter (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="366">Fl. Medit.</emphasis>
7: 43. 1997).
</paragraph>
